summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A KIDDY WORLD PLUS BOOSTER SEAT. UPON CONDUCTING RESEARCH, THE CONTACT NOTICED THAT THE SEAT WAS INCLUDED IN NHTSA CAMPAIGN NUMBER: 16C005000 (CHILD SEAT). WHEN THE CONTACT ATTEMPTED TO CALL THE MANUFACTURER, THEY DID NOT RECEIVE A RESPONSE. THE CONTACT STATED THAT THE MANUFACTURER EXCEEDED A REASONABLE AMOUNT OF TIME FOR THE REPAIR. THE PURCHASE DATE WAS UNKNOWN. THE CHILD SEAT HAD NOT EXPERIENCED A FAILURE.
